data.description: What a find in the City of Croswell! Cute single family home with a large yard that also includes a fenced in dog run. One car attached garage with interior and backyard access. This is almost a new house! Everything has been replaced and remodeled! New Windows 2023, New Roof and extra insulation 2019, New luxury tile Flooring Dec. 2023, remodeled bathroom, ALL Brand New 2023 Appliances are INCLUDED, New range hood fan,  even the brand new washer and dryer stay! New front door, New alarm system with hardwired smoke detectors. This home is waiting for you! Motivated Seller- Bring Offers!
